unilaterally control your own borders. \emph{Political Theory, 36}(1),
37--65. {[}\texttt{abizadeh2008border}. The all-subjected principle; a
democratic-boundary argument about human subjection. The machine
application is this corpus's extension, not Abizadeh's.{]}

